title: Your Baby Can Discover / Your Child Can Discover 6 DVDs Complete
description:
Your Child Can Discover! Math, Music, Colors, Shapes, Logic Patterns, and Prepositions! This deluxe kit includes all three Your Baby Can Discover (YBCD) DVDs and all three Your Child Can Discover (YCCD) DVDs.

This is Dr. Titzer's newest and favorite series of DVDs and books. The DVDs, audio CD, and books are designed to teach pitch in music, 96 different colors, geometric shapes, logic patterns, math concepts, and much more! This highly entertaining program uses a multi-sensory, interactive approach that encourages the child to participate and learn. Each DVD covers all of the topics and each one goes deeper into the concepts. While there is research showing that perfect pitch can be learned early in life the research was not done using Your Child Can Discover.
